author: Atomic Shrimp
description:
This was supposed to be a straightforward foraging video, but then there was cake, and then I had to run the dehydrator, then other things happened.  Scope Creep, they call it.  Nearly turned into Random Stuff all on its own.  There are chapters so you can skip anything you don't want, or find what you do want...

Join the Atomic Shrimp official Discord server for FREE early access to videos! - https://discord.gg/atomicshrimp  
Atomic Shrimp subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/AtomicShrimp/

Link to the study on the long-term effects of foraging: https://www.conservationevidence.com/individual-study/230

Link to the page with the full recipe for the cake:
https://atomicshrimp.com/post/2011/09/29/Boil-Bake-Fruit-Cake
